    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_3",
    "text": "1与玻璃面板平齐或突出的玻璃助：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09489916963226572,
      0.21700223713646533,
      0.3147489126136813,
      0.23937360178970918
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_10",
    "text": "8.1.1四边形玻璃面板可采用四点支承，有据时也可采用六 点支承；三角形玻璃面板可采用三点支承。玻璃面板支承孔边与 板边的距离不宜小于70mm。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5393436140767102,
      0.24161073825503357,
      0.918940292605773,
      0.3243847874720358
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_4",
    "text": "2后置或骑缝的玻璃助：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09648082245947015,
      0.2975391498881432,
      0.24990114669829971,
      0.319910514541387
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_11",
    "text": "8.1.2采用浮头式连接件的幕墙玻璃厚度不应小于6mm；果用 沉头式连接件的幕墙玻璃厚度不应小于8mm。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5377619612495057,
      0.3288590604026846,
      0.918940292605773,
      0.38031319910514544
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_5",
    "text": "式中 9 垂直于玻璃面板的分布荷载设计值（N/mm），抗震 设计时应包含地震作用计算的分布荷载设计值： I- 两肋之间的玻璃面板跨度（mm）； 1 胶建宽度，取表璃面板截面厚度（mm）： ——胶缝宽度，取玻璃肋截面厚度（mm)； f——硅酮结构密封胶在风荷载作用下的强度设计值， 取0.2N/mm²。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06959272439699486,
      0.37360178970917224,
      0.44918940292605775,
      0.5749440715883669
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_12",
    "text": "安装连接件的夹层玻璃和中空玻璃，其单片厚度也应符合上 述要求。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5393436140767102,
      0.3870246085011186,
      0.9173586397785686,
      0.436241610738255
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_13",
    "text": "8.1.3玻璃之间的空隙宽度不应小于10mm，且应果用硅酮建筑 密封胶嵌缝。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5377619612495057,
      0.4429530201342282,
      0.9173586397785686,
      0.49217002237136465
    ],
    "page": "book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_JGJ1022003_extracted_page_27_14",
    "text": "8.1.4点支承玻璃支承孔周边应进行可靠的密封。当点支承玻 璃为中空玻璃时，其支承孔周边应采取多道密封措施。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
